data.description: 7.44 acres of pure privacy, makes the perfect setting for your mini farm. No HOA, bring the chickens, cows, and horses. 3 total acres of pasture, split with 1 acre pin, and 2 acre pin. Master on Main, 4 car garage, open concept, and upper level loft.  Exterior features large covered rocking chair front porch, plantation shutters, and enormous party deck. Main level offers hard surface floors throughout, fresh paint, large laundry room with cabinets and drying rack, large country kitchen with breakfast bar, new counter tops, freshly painted cabinets, SS/black appliances, and large eat-in formal dining room.  Owner's suite boasts renovated bathroom, double vanity with tongue and groove accents, framed mirrors, upgraded faucets, separate soaking tub, double stand up shower, and double closet. Upper level is ready for entertainment with a open loft, and 2 secondary bedrooms.
